            <title>[SOLR-4071] CollectionsHandler.handleCreateAction() doesn&apos;t validate parameter count and type</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4071</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CollectionsHandler.handleCreateAction() doesn&apos;t validate parameter count and type. numShards&apos;s type doesn&apos;t checked and parameter count maybe less than required &lt;/p&gt;</description>
